- `TEXT(...,"yyyy-mm")` normalises dates to a year‑month string, allowing a simple equality test.  
- The boolean array (`TRUE`/`FALSE`) is coerced to 1/0 and multiplied by the sum of the two paycheck columns, giving the total for the matching month.  

